@base_url = http://localhost:8080
@jwt_token = <your_token_here>

### Get Profile
GET {{base_url}}/api/customers/me
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### Update Address
PUT {{base_url}}/api/customers/me
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "deliveryAddress": "456 New St",
  "city": "Abuja"
}
